name: FingerPunk #026 (Nurse Nara)
description: Nara is the resident nurse in the FingerPunk metaverse. She loves to mend wounds and comfort the sick. She has a pet project in Zed and has been trying to cure his condition. Nara has a bit of a crush on the Masked King and always tries to convince him to settle down and socialize with the other FingerPunks.
